yield: for 16g egg yolk
notes: |
  Base ratio 1 : 10 : 0.5 : 0.5 : 0.3 (egg yolk : oil : vinegar : lemon juice : dijon mustard).
  Masses below are that ratio scaled to a 16g egg yolk; seasoning is per 16g yolk.
ingredients:
  - item: egg yolk
    mass: 16
    qty: 1
    unit: ea
    basis: true
  - item: oil
    mass: 160
  - item: vinegar
    mass: 8
  - item: lemon juice
    mass: 8
  - item: dijon mustard
    mass: 4.8
  - item: salt
    mass: 2
  - item: msg
    mass: 0.5
  - item: garlic
    qty: 1
    unit: clove
    note: grated
steps:
  - mix egg yolk, salt, msg, and grated garlic in bottom of tall jug or carafe
  - start blending on egg yolk
  - slowly incorporate oil, vinegar, lemon juice, and dijon mustard
